args: Don't be shy there, lass! Come have a look\nat the latest fluffy candy sensation!
Come one, come all! No tricks or dark\nmagics here—just a genuine miracle\nunfolding before your very eyes!
I've never seen so many people...
It feels so strange to be in a place\nlike this while in human form.
Guess you don't get out much,\neh, Sophie?
Yeah, when we go into town, Sophie is\nusually in Joker's pho...er, his pocket.
Yeah, and you're usually in Joker's bag.
Hey, I take plenty of walks alone!\nBut Sophie doesn't really get to do that.
Yeah, opportunities to get out in the world\nare very precious to me, so thanks for this.
Well, we've got some time left, so where\ndo you want to head next, Sophie?
I hear there'll be a performance at the\ntheater today—and as luck would have it,\nthere is a new bakery across the street!
I appreciate the thought, but don't worry\nabout me.
I am humanity's companion.\nIf there's anything I can do to help,\nI want to do it.
Oh no! That old lady fell down!\nI should go check on her!
Are you all right, ma'am? Did you hurt your\nback? Here, allow me to help you up.
Aaand...HOOF! *phew* Oh, thank you.\nWhat a sweet young thing you are.
No prob. But you're clearly carrying\ntoo much. Here, I'll hold it for you.\nWhere do you need to go?
Land sakes! Well, if you really don't mind,\nI'm just headed to that store over there\nto meet up with my son.
All right, all loaded up. Hold my hand\nand we'll take it nice and slow.
There we go. I'll just set your things down.\nAnything else I can help with?
Oh, you've already done plenty, my dear!\nNow I won't be late. I feel like I should do\nsomething to thank you...
No prob. I'm humanity's\ncompanion, so your thanks are\nthe only reward I need.
Well then, I'll take my leave.\nTake care, child—and thank you again!
Did I do a good job?
It was my first time helping a stranger...\nand she thanked me...
Huh. I guess you don't really talk\nto anyone but us, do you?
Not usually, no. But now that she's got a\nhuman form, she can run around and do\nwhatever the heck she wants!
Yes! Now I can meet more people, talk to\nmore people, and most importantly,\nhelp more people.
I can do so much good!
Heh. You really are fond of lending\na hand where you can.

The only directive I'm able to recall is,
＂Become humanity's companion.＂
As an AI, it is my sole purpose for
existence.
So I want to be of use to people—\nand I want to learn as much as I\ncan about the human heart.

Well, if you like helping people,
you've fallen in with the right crowd!
And we've got more than enough heart
to go around!
In that case... I have a favor to ask of you,\n{player_name}.
Will you let me handle the next request\nthat comes into the Halidom?
It would be a precious chance for me\nto have more experiences like this one.
You got it, Sophie. The next request\nwe get is all yours.
Ha ha! Save your thanks for when I've\nactually done something. Good luck!
I like that enthusiasm! Oh, and I know\nyou'll be great, Sophie. Heck, you take\ncare of us all the time already!
Still, not having access to the internet\nhere might be a problem.
We better keep an eye on her in case she\nneeds backup. What do you say, Joker?
Hm-hm-hmmm! ♪ Even in this\nstrange world, I will be the finest\ncompanion I can be!
